title: Life | Pics: This couple's wedding photos accidentally got very NSFW very fast
text:
Ah, your big day. One of the most important things you'll ever experience in your life. Sure there's no better time to tell the world you like a bit of bondage.
Tying the knot obviously has a double meaning for this couple, or so their wedding photos would suggest, as according to this one they do some S&M.
Bless.
Via Reddit and Metro
